:: Doctor Harper's Office Trance
<<effects>>
<<pass 10>>
<<hypnotised 1>>
<<set $trance to 1>>

당신은 무아지경에 깊이 빠져든다. <span class="green"><<if $harper_appointments.hypnosis is 0 and $harper_appointments.dog is 0>>이 정도로 평온한 기분은 난생 처음이다.<<else>>당신은 익숙한 평온 속으로 빠져든다.<</if>></span> 하퍼의 목소리가 당신에게 흘러들어온다.
<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 5>>
	"That's very good. Now, the next time you feel overwhelmed by it all..." <span class="purple"><<his>> voice fades away, along with the rest of the room. Someone is standing where Harper just was.</span>
	<br><br>

	<span class="forest-green">It's Gwylan. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes a step towards you, smiling, and cups your cheeks. No words leave <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> lips, but they move regardless.</span>
	<br><br>

